  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 Tbsp of sesame oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the Sichuan peppercorns and cook for 10 seconds, until fragrant.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger, and cook for 10 seconds, until fragrant.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, Hunan chili bean paste, and cooked tofu, and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the coconut cream, soy sauce, and brown sugar, and stir-fry for 1-2 minutes, until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Stir in the chopped green onions and toasted peanuts.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the mapo tofu in a bento box, garnished with additional green onions and peanuts if desired.",
    "Serve immediately, with steamed rice or noodles if desired."
